Date: 1993-10-28

Title: Anyons as quon particles

Authors: V.Bardek, M.Doresic and S.Meljanac

Comments: 10 pages,Latex

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D49 (1994) 3059-3062

The momentum operator representation of nonrelativistic anyons is developedin the Chern - Simons formulation of fractional statistics. The connectionbetween anyons and the q-deformed bosonic algebra is established.